table_description: Details of mobile devices, including model, status, hardware, and software information.

columns.name: deviceId
columns.description: Unique device identifier.

columns.name: serialNumber
columns.description: The serial number of the device.

columns.name: status
columns.description: The current status of the device.

columns.name: lastSync
columns.description: Timestamp of the last device sync.

columns.name: supportEndDate
columns.description: The support end date for the device.

columns.name: model
columns.description: Model of the device.

columns.name: meid
columns.description: MEID number of the device.

columns.name: orderNumber
columns.description: Order number associated with the device.

columns.name: willAutoRenew
columns.description: Indicates if the device will auto-renew.

columns.name: osVersion
columns.description: The OS version installed on the device.

columns.name: platformVersion
columns.description: The platform version of the device.

columns.name: firmwareVersion
columns.description: The firmware version installed on the device.

columns.name: macAddress
columns.description: The MAC address of the device.

columns.name: bootMode
columns.description: The boot mode of the device.

columns.name: lastEnrollmentTime
columns.description: Timestamp when the device was last enrolled.

columns.name: kind
columns.description: The type of the device.

columns.name: recentUsers
columns.description: List of recent users associated with the device.

columns.name: activeTimeRanges
columns.description: Active time ranges associated with the device.

columns.name: lastKnownNetwork
columns.description: Last known network information for the device.

columns.name: systemRamTotal
columns.description: Total system RAM.

columns.name: diskVolumeReports
columns.description: Reports on the device's disk volumes.

columns.name: cpuStatusReports
columns.description: Reports on the CPU status.

columns.name: cpuInfo
columns.description: CPU information.

columns.name: deviceFiles
columns.description: List of device files.

columns.name: autoUpdateExpiration
columns.description: Expiration date for auto-update.

columns.name: ethernetMacAddress
columns.description: Ethernet MAC address.

columns.name: orgUnitPath
columns.description: Organizational unit path for the device.

columns.name: tpmVersionInfo
columns.description: TPM version details.

columns.name: osUpdateStatus
columns.description: Operating system update status.

columns.name: extendedSupportEligible
columns.description: Indicates if extended support is eligible.

columns.name: extendedSupportStart
columns.description: Start date of extended support.

columns.name: extendedSupportEnabled
columns.description: Indicates if extended support is enabled.

columns.name: fanInfo
columns.description: Information about the device's fan.

columns.name: backlightInfo
columns.description: Information about the device's backlight.
